cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.DL, cs.DB 

The paper discusses information integration applications and resource discovery, which are closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and data management (cs.DB). The use of social bookmarking sites also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and social networks (cs.SI). Finally, the paper mentions the hidden web, which is a topic in web search and data mining (cs.DL).
